    {
        "content": "<p><span aria-label=\"speech balloon\" class=\"emoji emoji-1f4ac\" role=\"img\" title=\"speech balloon\">:speech_balloon:</span> cfallin created <a href=\"https://github.com/bytecodealliance/wasmtime/pull/13667#discussion_r3423094963\">PR review comment</a>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>From a mini-language-design point of view: why not permit an empty list? Wouldn't that mean \"vmctx itself\"?</p>\n<p>(May not have a actual use so I'm fine constraining this, just curious if there was a deeper reason or contradiction here)</p>\n</blockquote>",
